{"tid":144891,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"條腰好痛，應該照XRAY定MRI","createTime":"2017-03-05T19:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:38:33.000Z","uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fcf90a012a8f20cdf141891bc261ff48f500b3","tid":144891,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:57:20.000Z","msg":"星咁的，小弟懷疑條腰出左事，GOOGLE SEARCGH 過徵狀，但分唔到係脊椎移位定係梨狀肌發炎，想問去睇既話應該照咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a89f879d6879df5c2f782d0fc9a9c3fb1f2d80e","tid":144891,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:59:28.000Z","msg":"你想睇政府定私家先<br />\n<br />\n政府的話應該係睇左普通科門診<br />\n確診左係咩病先<br />\n再轉介睇專科或者照野"},{"pid":"bc7ebdc54065d472b913ecf0623fb5f3a322a88d","tid":144891,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T20:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你想睇政府定私家先<br />\n<br />\n政府的話應該係睇左普通科門診<br />\n確診左係咩病先<br />\n再轉介睇專科或者照野</blockquote><br />\n政府門診應該有排等，我諗緊出去搵私家睇睇，又或者去學校診所睇左先，但私家照一次應該好那貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a047d01db23cbc2564912ae95f784077459009","tid":144891,"uid":36959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T20:43:34.000Z","msg":"形容下點痛"},{"pid":"d3a3b8dbb90801363b7c04fd834905d9ef8d3dac","tid":144891,"uid":86485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T22:34:30.000Z","msg":"係咪比肥婆女朋友坐到咁"},{"pid":"ed93e3f70ec1fac8154f6f7451209a6ba06a59d1","tid":144891,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T23:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪比肥婆女朋友坐到咁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係小肥靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f6b6b48401b2a1be505861388cc364d335a8e3","tid":144891,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T23:51:52.000Z","msg":"X光出去照最多400<br />\nMri講最少幾千<br />\n照撚完絕大部分情況無咩分別都係咁攪的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傷左條腰會好撚煩加無得點醫<br />\n自己小心"},{"pid":"59b1ba7adee317927359b74ed91baa2ea72111fc","tid":144891,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T23:54:45.000Z","msg":"MRI啦<br />\n後生通常係軟組織出事<br />\nXray未必睇到"},{"pid":"30b8dbe16fbcdfe5ab51042a6cd69c545d89bb84","tid":144891,"uid":74172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:04:02.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦，幫你做個test就分到"},{"pid":"dde7f075f6019bbf5ecda6b12ea839424d7518f5","tid":144891,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:07:32.000Z","msg":"冇買保險咩"},{"pid":"2706f57aaf325a0fccb6e2f2f015c11f1c92934d","tid":144891,"uid":82262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:46:09.000Z","msg":"Mri好撚平咋wor"},{"pid":"18836df3277c6694b710f3b9eaeffb5843bfdffa","tid":144891,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mri好撚平咋wor</blockquote><br />\n萬萬聲喎"},{"pid":"fbba20ebf45a8785dd2063ddc9468643c0aa9635","tid":144891,"uid":82523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:08:14.000Z","msg":"睇左醫生先<br />\n佢會答你照x ray定mri<br />\n<br />\n有醫生轉介既話照mri會平d<br />\n上次照條腰mri 用左千五"},{"pid":"b3e6e4e99e82e8d42424ad61b2e037fdfde5755b","tid":144891,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"練下瑜珈 蛇式 舒緩下"},{"pid":"27e27ad757a6243ca0135ba222cc339554394c08","tid":144891,"uid":37182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左醫生先<br />\n佢會答你照x ray定mri<br />\n<br />\n有醫生轉介既話照mri會平d<br />\n上次照條腰mri 用左千五</blockquote><br />\n你睇邊個醫生？<br />\n邊度照？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329fcd7780d4564f45a735561e45bf5caff9c05b","tid":144891,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:23:35.000Z","msg":"睇次私家再轉介政府覆診會快d"},{"pid":"45d1532802d8b4db9dd87394a1f9134fdbd49acd","tid":144891,"uid":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"認真 睇左骨科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常會同你做啲初步檢查<br />\n我半年前條腰尾龍骨個位都好撚痛<br />\n坐低一陣就會痛 諗住去照下<br />\n結果睇完醫生之後佢就斷左症<br />\n話唔洗晒錢去照 就算照左都只會照到同佢講嘅一樣<br />\n之後做左幾個月推拿+做啲佢比嘅運動練腰<br />\n依家基本上已經唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3adaca6d264027b49905a9d00dc6e31692661f","tid":144891,"uid":7138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"有冇買保險?<br />\n有就入院搞,留院2日一夜,Mri,物理治療3-4次,醫生費,藥費,2個月前浸會𠹺單12k . 我係腰椎盤凸出"},{"pid":"0616f8e0f8c616a78068c872ef2eec297d9e8a4a","tid":144891,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真 睇左骨科先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常會同你做啲初步檢查<br />\n我半年前條腰尾龍骨個位都好撚痛<br />\n坐低一陣就會痛 諗住去照下<br />\n結果睇完醫生之後佢就斷左症<br />\n話唔洗晒錢去照 就算照左都只會照到同佢講嘅一樣<br />\n之後做左幾個月推拿+做啲佢比嘅運動練腰<br />\n依家基本上已經唔痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打邊度做推拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84386f7caa87a788902d37e6f30055cb8a5c7976","tid":144891,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得唔係腎出事?"},{"pid":"9a0ef7b691d7189ce574c22b0f83b124eeecf375","tid":144891,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇買保險?<br />\n有就入院搞,留院2日一夜,Mri,物理治療3-4次,醫生費,藥費,2個月前浸會𠹺單12k . 我係腰椎盤凸出</blockquote><br />\n冇買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加點痛法呢，就係係右邊pat pat 裡面果舊骨痠痛出黎咁，平日行路坐低都唔覺痛，係訓低又或者抬右腳果陣會痛，難d發力，扯主扯主咁"},{"pid":"a257fc8c2c303c3fb08e0dde3b97215843356fdb","tid":144891,"uid":5777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇買保險?<br />\n有就入院搞,留院2日一夜,Mri,物理治療3-4次,醫生費,藥費,2個月前浸會𠹺單12k . 我係腰椎盤凸出</blockquote><br />\n冇買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加點痛法呢，就係係右邊pat pat 裡面果舊骨痠痛出黎咁，平日行路坐低都唔覺痛，係訓低又或者抬右腳果陣會痛，難d發力，扯主扯主咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無人知你買個時有無腰痛問題架嘛好似"},{"pid":"8ab6c12efd71b5beabffaf2d321651e8292c918d","tid":144891,"uid":7138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇買保險?<br />\n有就入院搞,留院2日一夜,Mri,物理治療3-4次,醫生費,藥費,2個月前浸會𠹺單12k . 我係腰椎盤凸出</blockquote><br />\n冇買保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加點痛法呢，就係係右邊pat pat 裡面果舊骨痠痛出黎咁，平日行路坐低都唔覺痛，係訓低又或者抬右腳果陣會痛，難d發力，扯主扯主咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d 似坐骨神經痛,不過都係搵醫生睇下咩事啦!"},{"pid":"ad48c306398ca9e3c8bac0f15a1709cb6df3415f","tid":144891,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"睇醫生先永遠無錯<br />\n<br />\nxray只睇到骨，作用有限<br />\n<br />\n要照就照MRI, 不過MRI太sensitive<br />\n照親實話有問題"},{"pid":"d6f195de8679d78b60f0606595b6ea031e14c4d9","tid":144891,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"排緊政府醫院MRI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}